类 PatchEntry

java.lang.Object
  org.crosswire.common.diff.PatchEntry
所有已实现的接口：
java.lang.Iterable<Difference>
public class PatchEntry
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<Difference>

A PatchEntry is a single "instruction" in a Patch, consisting of a interval over which differences are applied and the differences that should be applied. Based on the LGPL Diff_Match_Patch v1.5 javascript of Neil Fraser, Copyright (C) 2006
http://neil. fraser.name/software/diff_match_patch/
